# Shell & env
- Assume an activated micromamba env at `./.venv`. In terminals, activate with:
  `eval "$(micromamba shell hook -s bash)" && micromamba activate -p ./.venv`.
- Use the tasks "pytest", "lint", "format". Prefer `pytest -q`, `ruff check`, `black .`.
- Respect `.env` (loaded via direnv); never echo secret values.

